query:
SELECT
    DATE_TRUNC('day',u.created_at) AS "period",
    COUNT(DISTINCT u.user_id) AS "count!"
FROM user_course_settings u
WHERE u.current_course_id = $1
  AND u.deleted_at IS NULL
  AND NOT (u.user_id = ANY($2))
  AND u.created_at >= $3
  AND u.created_at <= $4
GROUP BY period
ORDER BY period
